Reverend and <normalised orig="worshipfull" auto="true">worshipful</normalised> M<hi rend="high">r</hi> Tho: Goad, D<hi rend="high">r</hi> of <normalised orig="Divinitie" auto="true">Divinity</normalised>, <lb/>
by whose labour this <normalised orig="worke" auto="true">work</normalised> is carefully corrected, <lb/>
