or his spits (that I may <normalised orig="vse" auto="true">use</normalised> <normalised orig="Origens" auto="false">Origins</normalised> notes) <normalised orig="haue" auto="true">have</normalised> <normalised orig="beene" auto="true">been</normalised> <lb/>
