and <normalised orig="shew" auto="true">show</normalised> feats by <normalised orig="actiuitie" auto="true">activity</normalised>, to <normalised orig="deceiue" auto="true">deceive</normalised> the simple. <normalised orig="Againe" auto="true">Again</normalised>, <lb/>
if some little thing be censured in the first inventor, I hope <lb/>
they that <normalised orig="loue" auto="true">love</normalised> him, will not <normalised orig="thinke" auto="true">think</normalised>, as good friends as they <lb/>
<normalised orig="deale" auto="true">deal</normalised> with him, like Gnatts, which after they <normalised orig="haue" auto="true">have</normalised> made <lb/>
